      <p class="l-sec-label">What Groundwork is</p>
      <h2 class="l-sec-h2" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 16px">Most tools ask everyone the same questions in the same room. This one doesn't.</h2>
      <p class="l-sec-p" style="margin:0 auto 16px;text-align:center;max-width:560px">Each person answers on their own, without seeing anyone else's responses. Nobody performs for the group. Nobody defers in the moment and disagrees later.</p>
      <p class="l-sec-p" style="margin:0 auto;text-align:center;max-width:560px">Groundwork compares every account and shows where they line up and where they quietly diverge. Nobody has to take anyone's word for it.</p>
